Kiki is a modified version of Wiki.js. Modifications include:
- Feature completion for the v3 alpha (page history, browse mode,
  3rd party authentication, password reset, editor enhancements,
  comments, search autocomplete, and more)
- Bug fixes (authentication strategy loading, deprecated dependencies,
  GraphQL schema type corrections)
- UI rebranding from Wiki.js to Kiki
- Modernization of server dependencies

The original Wiki.js source code is available at:
  https://github.com/requarks/wiki

